SATISFACTION-FILTER-LIMIT-INFO: Select a maximum of 31 days for the filter
SATISFACTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-FILTERS:
The satisfactions can be filtered through 2 fields:
  • Date – the date on which satisfaction was created.
  • Resolved – whether the virtual assistant was satisfactory or not for the user.
SATISFACTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-BULK: Show the volume of responses to the satisfaction survey.
SATISFACTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-EVOLUTI: Show satisfaction response response evolution over a range of dates.
SATISFACTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-SURVEY-: Show the latest user feedback comments regarding virtual assistant satisfaction.
SATISFACTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-SURVEY: Show the proportion of users' feedback rating relative to virtual assistant satisfaction.
SATISFACTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-RESOLVE: Show the volume of satisfaction responses in relation to whether the doubt has been resolved or not.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-FILTERS:
Questions can be filtered through 6 fields:
  • Word – words that users typed
  • Content – FAQ on which the user's question was directed
  • Date – the date the question was created
  • Channel Type – in which type of channel the question was generated
  • Channel – in which channel the question was generated
  • Questions – question that user made to virtual assistant
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-QUESTION-BU: Shows the total number of questions generated by the virtual assistant.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-QUESTION-EV: Show evolution of questions during a range of dates.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-ASK-STATUS: Show the total value of possible question types (General, Found, Chit Chat, Not Found).
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-DAILY-AVERA: Shows the average number of questions per session.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-QUESTION-CO: Shows the proportion of questions per channel.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-USERS-QUEST: Shows the last questions asked by the user and which channel came.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-SATISFACTIO: Shows the latest user feedback comments regarding virtual assistant satisfaction.
Shows the proportion of users' feedback rating relative to virtual assistant satisfaction.
QUESTION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-GRAPH-QUEST: Shows the amount of FAQ interactions that the user has traversed in a stream
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-FILTERS:
Sessions can be filtered through 3 fields:
  • Date – the date on which the session was
  • Channel – in which channel the session was generated
  • Channel Type – on which channel type the session was generated
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-GERERAL-DATA: Show summarized values of possible session types (Total Value, Informational, Transactional, Found, Not Found)
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-MONTH-PROJEC:
Show the projection of number of sessions at the end of the month.
  • not affected by date filter
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-DAILY-AVERAG:
Show the calculated average of the day for the current month.
  • not affected by date filter
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-CHANNEL-EVOL: Show session progress for each available channel in the base.
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-RANKING-TOP1: Show FAQ's ranking variations per week.
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-FAQ-TOP10: Show Top 10 variations of the session FAQs.
SESSION-TOOLTIP-DESCRIPTION-WORD-TOP10: Show variations of the most spoken words by users.
